246
00:20:16,411 --> 00:20:17,621
Hello?!

247
00:20:19,539 --> 00:20:21,416
Hop on to my cycle,

248
00:20:21,500 --> 00:20:23,085
I promise you the delights

249
00:20:23,168 --> 00:20:26,338
