outside the station...

886
01:07:27,764 --> 01:07:29,205
...win the Derby.

887
01:07:42,226 --> 01:07:43,728
I made you.

888
01:07:45,939 --> 01:07:47,732
I will break you.

889
01:07:58,275 --> 01:07:59,869
Go home, Lallanji.

890
01:08:01,830 --> 01:08:03,915
A storm threatens.

891
