1035
01:18:04,912 --> 01:18:08,749
how much force must
Tendulkar apply to hit a six?

1036
01:18:09,542 --> 01:18:10,543
Think.

1037
01:18:11,711 --> 01:18:14,380
The chicken Fugga stole?

1038
01:18:14,464 --> 01:18:15,590
