1042
01:18:32,440 --> 01:18:34,734
And two for Kishore.

1043
01:18:35,860 --> 01:18:37,862
And four for Kusum.

1044
01:18:38,488 --> 01:18:40,155
And eight for Aazan...

1045
01:18:40,406 --> 01:18:46,245
And so on and so on...

1046
01:18:46,328 --> 01:18:50,791
